{"tid":1927480,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"臨完場連入四球綠茵反勝太神奇","createTime":"2020-03-15T20:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T15:34:15.000Z","uid":6783,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6f5ec09c28b38f769737049d766c9657b5327592","tid":1927480,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T20:18:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20150411/53624373\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20150411%2F53624373&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvlcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=2ee3b70b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20150411%2F53624373&h=18ff246e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20150411/53624373</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本乙組聯賽周六的一場賽事，東京綠茵在主場以4:3擊敗榜尾的FC岐阜，一場比賽七個入球，絕對抵睇。不過如果你是主隊球迷，相信在目睹愛隊贏波前，隨時已經嚇死幾件，事關綠茵今仗踢了不足30分鐘，已經落後0:3，這個比數更一直維持至83分鐘仍無改變。但世事無絕對，綠茵由84分鐘開始，先後有三位球員士哥，其中扳平的一球已經是補時3分鐘才射入的，直至補時6分鐘，綠茵前鋒平本一樹更加梅開二度，助綠茵奇蹟以4:3反勝，全取3分。<br />\n<br />\n嘻嘻嘻嘻 <br />\n<br />\n我記得個陣岐阜話80分鐘提前結束啦<br />\n反正得返數字上既反勝機會"},{"pid":"78e5bda5314800a94616892a853ce2c17fcc774a","tid":1927480,"uid":127362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T20:19:40.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩係到想當年"},{"pid":"617d98cf734e9ab68f4370e051f1b31c340cd557","tid":1927480,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T20:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又改名"},{"pid":"6b933387ac251251624db90c68d4153a36b3b031","tid":1927480,"uid":6783,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"78e5bda5314800a94616892a853ce2c17fcc774a","tid":1927480,"uid":127362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T20:19:40.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩係到想當年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T20:21:46.000Z","msg":"隔離post有人比喻做踢波 <br />\n有一隊踢